Why Minumul?

We believe in the idea that less is more!

Many companies do a great job of offering a lot of filler just to bump up the price. We asked Why? Most small business' only need a handful of services to get payroll done right.

So we built a package around what you need to get payroll done right, and priced it accordingly.

Designed with
your time
in mind.

We designed our plateform to get you in & out. We like you, but know you have better things to do.

Sign up is simple & broken up into 3 steps. All we need are a couple of lines of Company, Tax, & Bank information.

Challenging ourselves to do it better.

We built in a time stamp system to allow your employees to clock in & out from wherever you want. You can easily set up our system on any of your devices to get you up and running in no time. This means running payroll is as simple as confirming the amount and you're off doing what you love most.
